name: Yee Mee Loo's
description: Acrylic painting on stretched canvas. Artist Ashley A. and The Artist looking at live fowl for sale for slaughter. Across the street from artists' haunt Yee Mee Loo's bar. In Chinatown near the L.A. Arts District before it became known and full of big galleries and expensive eateries, when it was still derelict. Provenance: Painting is owned by Richard W. of LA, Vancouver, B.C., now back in CA. Shown in L.A.
